trans-unit.source: Provides a component editor for <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpotCollection"></xref> objects in an <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.ImageMap"></xref> or a similar control.
trans-unit.target: Gir et komponent redigeringsprogram for <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpotCollection"> </xref> objekter i en <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.ImageMap"> </xref> eller lignende kontroll.

trans-unit.source: The HotSpotCollectionEditor class provides a user interface for editing the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpot> elements of the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpotCollection> object that is embedded in an <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ImageMap> or a similar control.
trans-unit.target: Klassen HotSpotCollectionEditor gir et brukergrensesnitt for redigering av <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpot>elementer i den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpotCollection>objekt som er innebygd i en <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ImageMap>eller lignende kontroll.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ImageMap> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpotCollection> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpot>

trans-unit.source: The HotSpotCollectionEditor is invoked by selecting the ellipsis button (**…**) on the **HotSpots** property in the visual designer's **Properties** grid.
trans-unit.target: HotSpotCollectionEditor aktiveres ved å klikke ellipsen (**... **) på den **soner** egenskap i den visuelle utformeren **Egenskaper** rutenett.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.HotSpotCollectionEditor.CanSelectMultipleInstances%2A> method always returns `false` to indicate that only one object can be selected at a time in the editor.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.HotSpotCollectionEditor.CanSelectMultipleInstances%2A>metoden returnerer alltid `false` til å angi at bare ett objekt kan velges om gangen i redigeringsprogrammet.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.HotSpotCollectionEditor.CanSelectMultipleInstances%2A>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.HotSpotCollectionEditor.CreateNewItemTypes%2A> method returns an array of types that the editor can create.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.HotSpotCollectionEditor.CreateNewItemTypes%2A>metoden returnerer en matrise av typene redigeringsprogrammet kan opprette.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.HotSpotCollectionEditor.CreateNewItemTypes%2A>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.HotSpotCollectionEditor.HelpTopic%2A> property returns the name of the Help topic that the editor displays.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.HotSpotCollectionEditor.HelpTopic%2A>egenskapen returnerer navnet på hjelpeemnet som viser redigeringsprogrammet.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.HotSpotCollectionEditor.HelpTopic%2A>

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.HotSpotCollectionEditor"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.HotSpotCollectionEditor"> </xref> klasse.

trans-unit.source: The .NET Framework internally constructs a new instance of the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.HotSpotCollectionEditor> class when you select the ellipsis button (**…**) on the **HotSpots** property in the visual designer's **Properties** grid, when designing an <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ImageMap> control or other control that encapsulates a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpotCollection> object.
trans-unit.target: .NET Framework internt bygger en ny forekomst av klassen <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.HotSpotCollectionEditor>Når du velger-knappen (**... **) på den **soner** egenskap i den visuelle utformeren **Egenskaper** rutenett når du utformer en <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ImageMap>kontroll eller andre kontroller innkapsler en <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpotCollection>objektet.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpotCollection> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ImageMap> </xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.HotSpotCollectionEditor>

trans-unit.source: The type of the collection to edit.
Gets a value indicating whether multiple <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpot"></xref> collection elements can be selected at one time.
trans-unit.target: Henter en verdi som angir om flere <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpot"> </xref> Samlingselementer kan velges om gangen.

trans-unit.source: The CanSelectMultipleInstances method always returns `false`; thus, only one <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpot> object can be selected at a time in the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.HotSpotCollectionEditor> object.
trans-unit.target: Metoden CanSelectMultipleInstances returnerer alltid `false`; derfor bare én <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpot>objekt kan velges om gangen i den <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.HotSpotCollectionEditor>objektet.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.HotSpotCollectionEditor> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpot>

trans-unit.source: Gets the multiple data types that the collection editor can create.
trans-unit.target: Henter datatypene flere redigeringsprogrammet for samlingen kan opprette.

trans-unit.source: The types that the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.HotSpotCollectionEditor> object can create are <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CircleHotSpot>, <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.RectangleHotSpot>, <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.PolygonHotSpot>, and others that can be derived from the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpot> class.
trans-unit.target: Typen som den <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.HotSpotCollectionEditor>objekt kan opprette er <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CircleHotSpot>, <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.RectangleHotSpot>, <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.PolygonHotSpot>, og andre som kan være avledet fra <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpot>klassen.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpot> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.PolygonHotSpot> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.RectangleHotSpot> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CircleHotSpot> </xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.HotSpotCollectionEditor>

trans-unit.source: A type array of the data types the <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.HotSpotCollectionEditor"></xref> can create.
trans-unit.target: En type matrise av datatyper i <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.HotSpotCollectionEditor"> </xref> kan opprette.

trans-unit.source: Gets the Help topic to display for the <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.HotSpotCollectionEditor"></xref> object.
trans-unit.target: Henter hjelpeemnet skal vises for den <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.HotSpotCollectionEditor"> </xref> objektet.

trans-unit.source: The HelpTopic property gets the name of the Help topic to display when the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.HotSpotCollectionEditor> dialog box **Help** button is clicked or when the **F1** key is pressed.
trans-unit.target: Egenskapen HelpTopic henter navnet på hjelpeemnet skal vises når det <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.HotSpotCollectionEditor>dialogboksen **hjelpe** -knappen eller når den **F1** tast.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.HotSpotCollectionEditor>

trans-unit.source: A string that specifies the Help topic to display.
trans-unit.target: En tekststreng som angir hjelpeemnet for å vise.
